[node name="RunningTextPart" parent="RunningTextBox" index="3" instance=ExtResource( 5 )]
text = "\"You shall always keep an eye on the screen, kid.\" Grandpa told me.

\"I'm already old and soon I will not be around anymore.

If someone calls for help, we need eyes on the monitor.
It's been a long time since it last came to life, but I'm sure we're not the last humans in this god-forsaken galaxy.\""

[node name="RunningTextPart2" parent="RunningTextBox" index="4" instance=ExtResource( 5 )]
text = "I'd been floating through space for what feels like ages with nothing to do. Being a galaxy guardian was lame.
      	  
But then it happened. I got a distress signal from a ship.
"

